Entre.
<i>[ Porta a ranger ]</i>


480
00:32:20.130 --> 00:32:23.967
<i>Sr. Bell.</i>
Sr. Hundert.


481
00:32:24.050 --> 00:32:26.261
Por favor, sente-se.

